de.hshl.obj.data.array

Class ArrayBuilder.Int

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hshl.obj.data.array.ArrayBuilder.Int
  • Enclosing class:
    ArrayBuilder

    public static final class ArrayBuilder.Int
extends java.lang.Object
    Like an ArrayList<Integer>, but avoids boxing primitives. "Generic" interface to enable producing primitive arrays of unknown size incrementally.
    Author:
    Johannes Vollmer
